text": "中国人民银行副行长邹澜 4 月 28 日在国新办新闻发布会上表示，今年一季度末，个人住房贷款余额 38 万亿，增加约 2200 亿元，与去年一季度相比同比多增超过 2000 亿元。 邹澜表示，将根据国内外经济形势和金融市场运行情况，适时降准降息，保持流动性充裕，发挥好货币政策工具箱总量和结构双重功能，创设新的结构性货币政策工具，围绕稳就业、稳增长的重点领域精准发力，做好金融支持。还在研究丰富政策工具箱，将适时推出增量政策，助力稳就业、稳企业、稳市场、稳预期。（央视新闻）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b9aeabe5df5ae1182b2ecd4582aed42d_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "55 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1900148634365985921"}}, "attached_info": "CkoItOii5/i9heJOEAMaCTExNDcxODg0MiCx6rvABjAAOO8BQAhyEzE5MDAxNDg2MzQzNjU5ODU5MjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1745888057.923405", "card_id": "Q_30651530", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 57}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "加拿大的石油储备世界第二，为什么大家似乎都关注中东的石油为多呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "加拿大是美国进口石油的最大来源国，可是媒体上经常提到美国是为了中东的石油而战，让人感觉中东才是最大的石油来源。如何解释这一貌似矛盾的现象？（出处：《第三次工业革命》2012 年 6 月第 1 版 P189)"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/881f9d64e8950f2c7bc308b4e7d9a029_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/30651530"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0ItOii5/i9heJOEAMaBzQ0NDI5Mzgg15aKqwUwADivB0AJcggzMDY1MTUzMHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1745888057.924100", "card_id": "Q_1899825409241093601", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80